webots_pkg.simple_mapper module

This simple mapper is loosely based on both the bitcraze cflib point cloud example https://github.com/bitcraze/crazyflie-lib-python/blob/master/examples/multiranger/multiranger_pointcloud.py and the webots epuck simple mapper example: https://github.com/cyberbotics/webots_ros2

webots_pkg.simple_mapper.MAP_RES = 0.1

WARNING: Simple_mapper is working, but only if the crazyflie is named /cf1
